caption:
Your Spleen Center influences not just your health awareness but your ability to let go of what no longer serves you. 

This guide explains how a defined Spleen brings immediate signals about what belongs in your life, while an undefined Spleen offers broader perception but might need more time to process letting go. 

Understanding your design helps you work with your natural intuitive pattern. 

Is your Spleen Center defined or undefined? Which part of this resonated with you the most? Share in a comment!
